    I[Worker Pool] --> G
    I --> J[Mark RUNNING + event]
    J --> K[Execute via Agency/Agent bridge]
    K --> L{Outcome}
    L -->|success| M[COMPLETED + result + event]
    L -->|error| N[FAILED + error + event]

    O[Recurring Planner] --> P[Parse schedule_expr]
    P --> Q[Generate next instance task]
    Q --> C

    R[Recovery on startup] --> C
    R --> S[Requeue stranded RUNNING/QUEUED]
```

Componenti proposti:

1. **SchedulerService (nuovo)**
   - API concreta di `scheduler.Scheduler`
2. **Dispatcher**
   - selezione task pronti (time + dependencies)
3. **Executor/Worker pool**
   - run task attraverso orchestrator/agency
4. **RecurringPlanner**
   - cron/interval parser + next run computation
5. **RecoveryManager**
   - startup scan + reconciliation stati
6. **EventPublisher**
   - bridge DB events -> subscribers in-memory

